Binary Tree-A directed tree where each node having 0,1,2 nodes.nodes are called left and right node.

Class function to create a Node of Tree-
     
        Class Node
             {
               public:
               int data;
               Node* left, right;
               Node(int x)
               {  
                  data=x;
                   left=right=NULL;

                }

              };


There are 2 types of traversals-
1. Depth first Search(inorder,preorder,postorder)
2. Breath first Search



